 29 | ### Current Architecture (Python-Controlled)
 30 | 
 31 | ```
 32 | ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
 33 | │ 1. GAZEBO HARMONIC (Physics Simulation)                        │
 34 | │    - DART physics engine (4ms timestep)                         │
 35 | │    - 8-DOF humanoid model (ArduBiped_Proto)                     │
 36 | │    - Joint position controllers (PID: P=8, I=0.01, D=10)        │
 37 | │    - IMU sensor on torso (1000 Hz)                              │
 38 | └────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
 39 |                  │
 40 |                  ├─ IMU data (JSON) ──────────────────────┐
 41 |                  │                                         │
 42 |                  ├─ Joint commands (Gazebo topics) ◄──────┤
 43 |                  │   /l_hip_pitch/cmd                     │
 44 |                  │   /r_hip_pitch/cmd                     │
 45 |                  │   /l_knee/cmd                          │
 46 |                  │   /r_knee/cmd                          │
 47 |                  │   /l_ankle/cmd (fixed joint)           │
 48 |                  │   /r_ankle/cmd (fixed joint)           │
 49 |                  │                                         │
 50 | ┌────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
 51 | │ 2. ARDUPILOT PLUGIN (ArduPilotPlugin in model.sdf)             │
 52 | │    - Receives IMU data from Gazebo                              │
 53 | │    - Sends to ArduPilot via JSON (127.0.0.1:9002)               │
 54 | │    - Receives servo PWM from ArduPilot (channels 0-3)           │
 55 | │    - Converts PWM → joint angles via multiplier/offset          │
 56 | │    - Publishes to Gazebo joint topics                           │
 57 | │                                                                  │
 58 | │    PWM Conversion Formula:                                       │
 59 | │    angle = (pwm - 1500) / 500 * multiplier + offset            │
 60 | │                                                                  │
 61 | │    Channel Mapping:                                              │
 62 | │    CH0 → l_hip_pitch  (mult=1.571, offset=-0.5)                │
 63 | │    CH1 → r_hip_pitch  (mult=1.571, offset=-0.5)                │
 64 | │    CH2 → l_knee       (mult=2.618, offset=-0.5)                │
 65 | │    CH3 → r_knee       (mult=2.618, offset=-0.5)                │
 66 | └────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
 67 |                  │
 68 |                  │ JSON Protocol (IMU → ArduPilot)
 69 |                  │ JSON Protocol (Servo PWM ← ArduPilot)
 70 |                  │
 71 | ┌────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
 72 | │ 3. ARDUPILOT ROVER SITL (Flight Controller)                    │
 73 | │    - EKF3 sensor fusion (AHRS_EKF_TYPE=10)                      │
 74 | │    - Attitude estimation from IMU                                │
 75 | │    - Servo output channels (SRV_Channels)                        │
 76 | │    - MAVLink telemetry (UDP:14551)                               │
 77 | │    - Lua scripting capability (SCR_ENABLE=1, not used yet)      │
 78 | └────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
 79 |                  │
 80 |                  │ MAVLink (UDP:14551)
 81 |                  │ ATTITUDE messages (pitch, roll, yaw)
 82 |                  │
 83 | ┌────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
 84 | │ 4. PYTHON GAIT CONTROLLER (gait_controller.py)                 │
 85 | │    - Reads ATTITUDE messages via pymavlink                       │
 86 | │    - Implements balance PID (Kp=0.08, Ki=0.001, Kd=0.01)        │
 87 | │    - Generates gait phases (6-phase walking cycle)               │
 88 | │    - Sends joint commands directly to Gazebo topics              │
 89 | │    - BYPASSES ArduPilot servo output entirely                    │
 90 | └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
 91 | ```
